        <updateDate>2017-09-28T15:44:01Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Former Presidents Amendment Act</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Former Presidents Act of 1958 to provide that former Presidents may not receive government funded office space, staff, or free use of the mail.</p> <p>Any unobligated amounts available for office space or staff of former Presidents are rescinded. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
